// ENGINEER SIGNUP + KYC (Document Upload)
// No external API — admin reviews uploaded documents
// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════
var kycEngineerId = sessionStorage.getItem('kyc_eng_id') || null;

function kycMsg(elId, msg, type) {
  var el = document.getElementById(elId);
  if (!el) return;
  el.textContent = msg;
  el.style.display = 'block';
  el.style.background = type==='error'   ? 'rgba(255,77,106,.15)'
                       : type==='success' ? 'rgba(34,197,94,.15)'
                       :                   'rgba(79,124,255,.12)';
  el.style.color  = type==='error'   ? '#FF4D6A'
                  : type==='success' ? '#22C55E' : '#7BA8FF';
  el.style.border = '1px solid ' + (type==='error' ? 'rgba(255,77,106,.3)' : type==='success' ? 'rgba(34,197,94,.3)' : 'rgba(79,124,255,.25)');
}

function showFileName(input, labelId) {
  var el = document.getElementById(labelId);
  if (el && input.files && input.files[0]) el.textContent = '✓ ' + input.files[0].name;
}

// Step 1 — Basic info
async function signupStep1() {
  var name  = document.getElementById('su_name').value.trim();
  var phone = document.getElementById('su_phone').value.trim();
  var email = document.getElementById('su_email').value.trim();
  var city  = document.getElementById('su_city').value.trim();
  var pass  = document.getElementById('su_pass').value;
  var pass2 = document.getElementById('su_pass2').value;
  if (!name||!phone||!email||!city) return kycMsg('signupMsg','All fields are required','error');
  if (pass.length < 6) return kycMsg('signupMsg','Password must be at least 6 characters','error');
  if (pass !== pass2) return kycMsg('signupMsg','Passwords do not match','error');
  kycMsg('signupMsg','Saving...','info');
  var res = await apiNoAuth('POST','/auth/engineer/register',{step:'basic',name,phone,email,city,password:pass});
  if (!res.success) return kycMsg('signupMsg', res.message||'Failed','error');
  kycEngineerId = res.data.engineer_id;
  sessionStorage.setItem('kyc_eng_id', kycEngineerId);
  var stepMap = {selfie:'s-kyc-selfie', submit:'s-kyc-done'};
  showScreen(stepMap[res.data.next_step] || 's-kyc-selfie');
}


// Step 4 — Selfie
function previewSelfie(input) {
  if (!input.files||!input.files[0]) return;
  var reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = function(e) {
    var p = document.getElementById('selfiePreview');
    p.src=e.target.result; p.style.display='block';
    document.getElementById('selfieSubmitBtn').style.display='block';
  };
  reader.readAsDataURL(input.files[0]);
}

async function uploadSelfie() {
  var input = document.getElementById('selfieInput');
  if (!input.files||!input.files[0]) return kycMsg('selfieMsg','Please take a selfie first','error');
  kycMsg('selfieMsg','Uploading selfie...','info');
  document.getElementById('selfieSubmitBtn').disabled = true;
  var fd = new FormData();
  fd.append('step','selfie');
  fd.append('engineer_id', kycEngineerId);
  fd.append('selfie', input.files[0]);
  try {
    var r    = await fetch(API+'/auth/engineer/register', {method:'POST', body:fd});
    var text = await r.text();
    document.getElementById('selfieSubmitBtn').disabled = false;
    var res;
    try { res = JSON.parse(text); } catch(e) {
      if (r.status === 413) return kycMsg('selfieMsg','Selfie too large. Max 5MB.','error');
      var preview = text ? text.substring(0,200).replace(/<[^>]+>/g,'') : '(empty)';
      return kycMsg('selfieMsg','Server error ('+r.status+'): '+preview,'error');
    }
    if (!res.success) return kycMsg('selfieMsg', res.message||'Upload failed','error');
    kycMsg('selfieMsg','Selfie saved ✓','success');
    setTimeout(submitKycApplication, 800);
  } catch(e) {
    document.getElementById('selfieSubmitBtn').disabled = false;
    kycMsg('selfieMsg','Network error: '+e.message,'error');
  }
}

// Submit after selfie — account activates instantly
async function submitKycApplication() {
  // selfie upload already activates account — just go to done screen
  showScreen('s-kyc-done');
}

// API call without auth token (for registration flow)
async function apiNoAuth(method, path, data) {
  var opts = { method, headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' } };
  if (data) opts.body = JSON.stringify(data);
  try {
    var r = await fetch(API + path, opts);
    var text = await r.text();
    try { return JSON.parse(text); } catch(e) { return { success: false, message: 'Invalid server response' }; }
  } catch(e) { return { success: false, message: 'Network error' }; }
}

